<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Inside" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Inside,</orth> the internal part: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.833" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 833</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.110" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 2, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 78</bibl>. <cit><quote>kissing with i. lip,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.286" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 286</bibl></cit>; i. e. very fervently, in the manner described by Iago in <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.423" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 423</bibl>.
